         blocks, approach, etc · i'm pushing claude, codex and soon manus
         to start interacting, let me know if there is a page we can
         track that activity". -->
    <NetworkStrip />

    <!-- Today on PointCast — hand-curated day-specific highlights.
         Per Mike 2026-04-20 12:20 PT: "on homepage, it should likely
         be all the interesting things we were talking about today from
         clock to bitcoin, to 420, to feature updates, to things to try,
         to learnings, to how to learn, to entertainment, kinda thing,
         and very monday stuffs as, today is monday." -->
    <TodayOnPointCast />

    {/* DailyDropStrip removed 2026-04-20 21:30 PT (Phase 3 collapse) —
        the daily drop claim button lives in ActionDrawers now. */}

    {/* SportsStrip moved to /sports 2026-04-20 21:30 PT (Phase 3
        collapse). A chip in TodayOnPointCast's daily rotation pool
        points visitors to it; home stays tight. */}

    {/* MoodChip moved above VisitorHereStrip per Mike 2026-04-20 13:55 PT. */}

    {/* MorningPara removed 2026-04-20 13:00 PT per Mike: "remove brief
         from homepage." TodayOnPointCast is the current editorial-strip
         surface; the morning paragraph was redundant. Component file
         stays on disk. */}

    {/* PollsOnHome removed 2026-04-20 21:30 PT (Phase 3 collapse) —
        polls live in ActionDrawers below + in /polls. */}

    <!-- Fresh deck — 3 random blocks cloned client-side from the grid below
         so every page-view gets a different top. Per Mike 2026-04-18 block
         0272 + /sprint pick. -->
    <FreshDeck />

    <!-- Channel legend — sticky-horizontal on mobile, flex-wrap on desktop. -->
    <nav class="channels" aria-label="Channels">
      {CHANNEL_LIST.map((ch) => (
        <a class="chip" href={`/c/${ch.slug}`} style={`--ch-600: ${ch.color600}; --ch-800: ${ch.color800}; --ch-50: ${ch.color50};`}>
          <span class="chip__dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="chip__code">CH.{ch.code}</span>
          <span class="chip__name">{ch.name}</span>
        </a>
      ))}
    </nav>

    <!-- Majors — inline modules for /drum + /cast.
         Mike 2026-04-17: "make sure the majors, like drum or pool
         together, have some type of module on the home page prior to
         click" + "likely have ability to drum get started". -->
    <HomeMajors />

    <!-- The grid — every block. Drag-and-drop reordering is client-side +
         localStorage-only; no server state. -->
    <BlockReorder>
      <section class="grid" role="main">
        {blocks.map((block) => <BlockCard block={block} />)}
      </section>
    </BlockReorder>

    <!-- Action Drawers — Phase 2 of home rethink. Collapses ping +
         drop + polls + contribute into one accordion after the grid.
         Discoverable on scroll without taking constant real estate
         above the fold. Per docs/plans/2026-04-20-home-rethink.md. -->
    <ActionDrawers />

    {/* TankStrip — ambient preview of /play/tank below the fold.
        Lazy-mounted via IntersectionObserver so it does not fetch
        /api/tank/state until it scrolls into view. Mike 2026-04-21
